### Create license (ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/licenses/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "typeId": "{{typeId}}",
  "ownerId": {{ownerId}},
  "deviceCount": 2,
  "description": "Test license"
}

### Activate license
POST http://localhost:8080/api/licenses/activate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "activationKey": "{{activationKey}}",
  "deviceName": "Laptop",
  "deviceMac": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF"
}

### Check license
POST http://localhost:8080/api/licenses/check
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "deviceMac": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF"
}

### Renew license
POST http://localhost:8080/api/licenses/renew
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "activationKey": "{{activationKey}}",
  "deviceMac": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF"
}
